## ðŸ§  Working Principle

1. Sensors continuously monitor the environment.
2. Arduino processes readings and compares them with safe thresholds.
3. On detection, GSM sends SMS while buzzer/LED give local alert.
4. Data uploaded to Firebase through Flask server for dashboard visualization.
5. User can view live readings and past events remotely.

